      <action-desc>
        <sponsor name-id="S327">Mr. Warner</sponsor> introduced the following bill; which was read twice and referred to the <committee-name committee-id="SSBK00">Committee on Banking, Housing, and Urban Affairs</committee-name>
      </action-desc>
